snippet.title: Among Us - Polus Map Trailer
snippet.description:
Polus is the third map for Among Us. It features a large map with new tasks and sabotages. It will be available on November 12, 2019, and cost $4. Online games will require each player to own the map. Local games only require the host to own the map.

iOS - https://apple.co/2Ms822h
Android - https://bit.ly/2sVMTFt
itch.io - https://innersloth.itch.io/among-us
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/945360/

Follow us on Twitter!
https://twitter.com/InnerslothDevs
